# http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7068179/convert-line-endlings-for-whole-directory-tree-git
# Fixing Error:
# fatal: CRLF would be replaced by LF in

# You need to install dos2unix if not already
# Run the following command at the top level of your git directory.
$ find . -type f | xargs dos2unix

----------------------------------------------------------------

# Not able to push the edited file in github
# http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7818963/not-able-to-push-the-edited-file-in-github
# Note that for a repo where you are declared as collaborator, you need to use a "Read+Write access" url:

https://UserName@github.com/Name/repoName

In other words, not an http address, but an https one.

----------------------------------------------------------------

# How to update Editor for Git?
# http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2596805/how-do-i-make-git-use-the-editor-of-my-choice-for-commits
$ sudo update-alternatives --config editor
OR
$ git config --global core.editor "vim"

